<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="bn">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>For My Pakhi ❤️</title>

<style>
*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:sans-serif;
}

body{
background:#000;
color:white;
text-align:center;
overflow-x:hidden;
}

h1{
margin-top:20px;
font-size:40px;
color:#ff4d6d;
}

.slider{
width:90%;
max-width:400px;
margin:25px auto;
}

.slider img{
width:100%;
border-radius:20px;
box-shadow:0 0 20px pink;
animation:fade 16s infinite;
position:absolute;
left:0;
right:0;
margin:auto;
opacity:0;
}

.slider img:nth-child(1){animation-delay:0s;}
.slider img:nth-child(2){animation-delay:4s;}
.slider img:nth-child(3){animation-delay:8s;}
.slider img:nth-child(4){animation-delay:12s;}

@keyframes fade{
0%{opacity:0;}
10%{opacity:1;}
25%{opacity:1;}
35%{opacity:0;}
100%{opacity:0;}
}

.message{
margin-top:520px;
padding:20px;
font-size:22px;
line-height:40px;
}

button{
margin-top:30px;
padding:18px 40px;
font-size:22px;
background:#ff0066;
border:none;
border-radius:50px;
color:white;
cursor:pointer;
}

#final{
display:none;
margin-top:80px;
font-size:35px;
color:pink;
animation:zoom 1.5s infinite;
}

@keyframes zoom{
50%{
transform:scale(1.1);
}
}

.heart{
position:fixed;
color:red;
font-size:25px;
animation:fall linear infinite;
}

@keyframes fall{
0%{
transform:translateY(-100px);
}
100%{
transform:translateY(100vh);
}
}
</style>

</head>

<body>

<h1>For My Pakhi ❤️</h1>

<div class="slider">
<img src="1.jpg">
<img src="2.jpg">
<img src="3.jpg">
<img src="4.jpg">
</div>

<div class="message">
পাখি, 💗💗<br><br>

তুমি আমার জীবনের সেই আলো,<br>
যা অন্ধকার দূর করে মনের মাঝে সুখ এনে দেয়।<br><br>

তোমার এই ভালোবাসা নিয়েই আমি<br>
সারাজীবন বেঁচে থাকতে চাই। ☺️❤️
</div>

<button onclick="showLove()">Click Here ❤️</button>

<div id="final">
💍<br><br>

Will You Stay With Me Forever? ❤️<br><br>

I Love You Pakhi 💗
</div>

<audio autoplay loop>
<source src="music.mp3">
</audio>

<script>

function showLove(){
document.getElementById("final").style.display="block";
}

setInterval(function(){

let heart=document.createElement("div");

heart.className="heart";

heart.innerHTML="❤️";

heart.style.left=Math.random()*100+"vw";

heart.style.animationDuration=(Math.random()*3+2)+"s";

document.body.appendChild(heart);

setTimeout(()=>{
heart.remove();
},5000);

},250);

</script>

</body>
</html>